{"tid":2167802,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"麥佳亞酒吧外和英國遊客發生衝突，被帶到警局","createTime":"2020-08-21T10:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T10:38:37.000Z","uid":30768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"858b77d9c525b27a347a72c36b5478da01291cb9","tid":2167802,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:37:36.000Z","msg":"據希臘媒體protothema報導，曼聯中堅麥佳亞在米克諾斯島度假時，因為和他人起衝突被捕了。<br />\n<br />\n當地時間今天早些時候，麥佳亞和他的朋友一起，在酒吧外與其他英國遊客發生了衝突。<br />\n<br />\n警察趕到後，麥佳亞等人和警察發生了口頭和肢體的衝突。不過隨後警方控制住了麥佳亞等人，平息了衝突，發生衝突的一行人都被帶到了當地警局。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EBAV5m7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEBAV5m7.jpg&h=da4690b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fe9d4f2e7244a520aefa0fbc179f95fde4d3af1","tid":2167802,"uid":134546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:38:23.000Z","msg":"打狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db846745a4121deeba4662f901df1d5ce047d666","tid":2167802,"uid":31314,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:38:37.000Z","msg":"魔性澎湃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}